snippet.title: ROVA - Pre-Alpha Demo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
ROVA: A Cosy Space-Rover Photography Game. 
► Wishlist on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2930130/ROVA

Help a new space colony conduct research on large spherical planets, by documenting elements of alien worlds through photography.


To Follow the games' development, check out our socials below!
